OL,3,CCat cafe 'the puurrfect way to reduce
OL,4,Cyour stress levels'
OL,6,FThe only cat cafe on the island of
OL,7,FIreland is about to open in east
OL,8,FBelfast.
OL,10,FOwner Dr Karen Galway said it's the
OL,11,Fpuuurfect way to reduce your stress
OL,12,Flevels and help with your mental well
OL,13,Fbeing."
OL,15,FJust being in the presence of cats is
OL,16,Freally good for your well being, it
OL,17,Fcan reduce your stress levels and
OL,18,Fincrease your Serotonin levels which
OL,19,Fis a feel good hormone".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
