OL,3,CCat cafe 'the puurrfect way to reduce
OL,4,Cyour stress levels'
OL,6,FThere are 11 beautiful cats in the
OL,7,Frescue led Kumiko Cat Lounge. They
OL,8,Fhave all come from Belfast Kitten
OL,9,Frescue and the hope is that they will
OL,10,Feventually find a forever home.
OL,12,FYou will have an option to adopt a cat
OL,13,Fif you fall in love ... and you will!
OL,15,F"The most important part has to the
OL,16,Fwelfare of the cats. A really
OL,17,Fimportant part was the partnership
OL,18,Fwith Belfast Kitten rescue.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
