OL,3,CCat cafe 'the puurrfect way to reduce
OL,4,Cyour stress levels'
OL,6,FIf there is a cat here we thought
OL,7,Fwould cope and they are not coping
OL,8,Fthey will go back to the rescue. These
OL,9,Fcats need home and there are hundreds
OL,10,Fof cats across Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FOur rescue centres are busting at the
OL,13,Fseams." said Dr Galway
OL,15,FIn a statement Cats Protection say
OL,16,Fthey take strong stance against cat
OL,17,Fcafes.
