OL,3,CCat cafe 'the puurrfect way to reduce
OL,4,Cyour stress levels'
OL,6,F"Cat cafes can be extremely stressful
OL,7,Ffor cats, as they are solitary animals
OL,8,Fby nature and do not generally choose
OL,9,Fto live in social groups.
OL,11,FThis means that the enforced proximity
OL,12,Fto many other cats and having to share
OL,13,Ffood, water and hiding and sleeping
OL,14,Flocations can cause stress and anxiety.
OL,16,FCats depend upon a predictable, stable
OL,17,Fenvironment. Cat cafes can be
OL,18,Funsettling for cats, with different
OL,19,Fpeople coming and going and with
OL,20,Fstrange smells and noises encroaching
OL,21,Fon their sense of security.
OL,26,@nD@IrryD@Urr
