OL,3,CCat cafe 'the puurrfect way to reduce
OL,4,Cyour stress levels'
OL,6,F"Karen is urging anyone who wants to
OL,7,Fcome and meet the cats to book online
OL,8,Fas there is a strict limit on the
OL,9,Fnumber of people allowed inside at one.
OL,11,FAnd for those who don't like cats ...
OL,12,Fwell that says more about you!
